{"id":305824,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/global-voices-正名活动：是colombia，不是columbia/","date":"2013-07-27T02:15:13Z","modified":"2013-07-27T02:15:13Z","title":"Global Voices | 正名活动：是Colombia，不是Columbia","content":"<p><p>为了以正视听并修正英语系国家常见的拼字错误，四位来自<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.zemoga.com/\">Zemoga</a>数位创新公司的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/02/22/its-colombia-not-columbia-a-social-media-campaign-changing-the-image-of-a-country_n_2743909.html?ncid=edlinkusaolp00000003\">Colombia年轻专家</a>，发起了“是Colombia，不是Columbia”的社群媒体活动。</p>\n<p>Richard Emblin在一篇发表于新闻网站<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://thecitypaperbogota.com/opinion/columbia-vs-colombia/\">The City Paper</a>的文章中解释：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>地理上来看，我们与英属Columbia州相距甚远；也远非“Columbia号”2003年在美国德州上空爆炸解体后，服役多年的太空梭。然而，许多人还是会将这两个地名搞错。Colombia并没有洛矶山脉，只有安地斯山脉。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>不过，活动任务不仅是要让人们正确拼出Colombia这个国家名称而已。Paul Giles在<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://seecolombia.travel/blog/2013/02/its-colombia-not-columbia/\">Colombia Travel blog</a>中提到：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“是Colombia，不是Columbia”这场正名运动，刚好证实并凸显出，拼错国名会让大众对这美好国家产生偏见。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>活动创始人之一的Emilio Pombo，告诉<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://nbclatino.com/2013/02/21/its-colombia-not-columbia-media-campaign-hopes-to-correct-common-mistake-of-countrys-name/#.USaujAg3XYV.twitter\">NBC Latino</a>的记者Edgar Zúñiga：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“我们注意到这个常见的错误，也了解到这是一个让全球能重新了解我国观感的平台。&#8230; 最近我们国家也发生了很棒的事情。Colombia成为一个旅游终点，并跃上世界舞台。我们想凸显这一点，而这一切将从把我们国家名称拼对开始。”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/silvia-vinas/\" title=\"文章导读 Silvia Viñas\">Silvia Viñas</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/02/25/get-it-right-its-colombia-not-columbia/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/07/27/12742/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AFColombia%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFColumbia&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12742%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12742%2F&#038;desc=%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AFColombia%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFColumbia\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12742%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12742%2F&#038;text=%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AFColombia%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFColumbia&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12742%2F&#038;title=%E6%AD%A3%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AFColombia%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFColumbia\" title=\"reddit\"><s